## âš™ï¸ 1. Where Nginx Is Commonly Used

| Use Case                                         | Description                                                             | Example                                    |
| ------------------------------------------------ | ----------------------------------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------ |
| **1ï¸âƒ£ Web Server**                               | Serves static content (HTML, CSS, JS, images) directly.                 | Host websites or dashboards.               |
| **2ï¸âƒ£ Reverse Proxy**                            | Forwards client requests to backend servers (C++, Node.js, Java, etc.). | `nginx` â†’ `127.0.0.1:8080` app             |
| **3ï¸âƒ£ Load Balancer**                            | Distributes traffic among multiple backend servers.                     | Balance across microservices.              |
